 \lim_{m\to \infty}\sum_{n=1}^{\infty}\frac{m}{m^2+n^2}=\int_{0}^\infty\frac{1}{1+x^2} 
 \sum_{n=1}^\infty\frac{m}{m^2+n^2}=\sum_{n=1}^{\infty}\frac{1}{1+(n/m)^2}\frac{1}{m} 
\int_{0}^\infty \frac{1}{1+x^2}\ dx:=\lim_{a \to \infty}\int_{0}^a \frac{1}{1+x^2}\ dx
