(0,\infty)
\lim_{n \to \infty}\sum_{t=1}^{\infty}{1 \over n}f\bigg({t \over n}\bigg)
\int_0^\infty f(x)\ dx=\lim_{N \to \infty}\int_0^N f(x)\ dx=\lim_{n,N\to \infty}\sum_{t=1}^{Nn}{1 \over n}f\bigg({t \over n}\bigg)
a:=\lim_{n,N\to \infty}\sum_{t=1}^{Nn}{1 \over n}f\bigg({t \over n}\bigg), b:=\lim_{n \to \infty}\sum_{t=1}^{\infty}{1 \over n}f\bigg({t \over n}\bigg)
